  "text": "In the future, we would like to incorporate the neighbor selection idea into our training framework, such as, importance pooling in [CITATION_1] ) which takes into account the importance of neighbors when aggregating the vector representations of neighbors. We would also like to extend our model to be scalable with larger knowledge graphs encouraged by the results in [CITATION_2] .",
